### 课程多教师课时费功能测试

### 1. 创建支持多教师教学的课程（每个教练不同课时费）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "多教师大课测试-不同课时费",
  "typeId": 3,
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "unitHours": 2.0,
  "price": 200.00,
  "coachFee": 50.00,
  "isMultiTeacher": true,
  "coachFees": [
    {
      "coachId": 1,
      "coachFee": 90.00
    },
    {
      "coachId": 2,
      "coachFee": 95.00
    },
    {
      "coachId": 3,
      "coachFee": 95.00
    }
  ],
  "campusId": 1,
  "description": "这是一个支持多教师教学的大课，每个教练课时费不同"
}

### 2. 创建单教师课程（使用默认课时费）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "单教师一对一课程-默认课时费",
  "typeId": 2,
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "unitHours": 1.0,
  "price": 300.00,
  "coachFee": 100.00,
  "isMultiTeacher": false,
  "coachFees": [
    {
      "coachId": 1,
      "coachFee": 100.00
    }
  ],
  "campusId": 1,
  "description": "这是一个单教师的一对一课程，使用默认课时费"
}

### 3. 查询课程列表（验证多教师教学字段和教练课时费）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 获取课程详情（验证多教师教学字段和教练课时费）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/detail?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 更新课程为多教师教学（修改教练课时费）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "更新后的多教师课程-新课时费",
  "typeId": 3,
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "unitHours": 2.0,
  "price": 250.00,
  "coachFee": 60.00,
  "isMultiTeacher": true,
  "coachFees": [
    {
      "coachId": 1,
      "coachFee": 85.00
    },
    {
      "coachId": 2,
      "coachFee": 90.00
    },
    {
      "coachId": 3,
      "coachFee": 92.00
    }
  ],
  "campusId": 1,
  "description": "更新后的多教师课程，调整了教练课时费"
}

### 6. 更新课程为单教师教学（移除多教师设置）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 2,
  "name": "更新后的单教师课程",
  "typeId": 2,
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "unitHours": 1.0,
  "price": 350.00,
  "coachFee": 120.00,
  "isMultiTeacher": false,
  "coachIds": [1],
  "campusId": 1,
  "description": "更新后的单教师课程描述"
}

### 7. 再次获取课程详情（验证更新后的教练课时费）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/detail?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

